Rule 34
}}}
{\f2 \strike0 \ul0 \b0 \sa0 \sb200 \fs20 \cf1 \i0 
 and on \u8216\'3fShowing good cause therefor\u8217\'3f the court may order their inspection, copying or photographing. No such application has here been made; the demand is made on the basis of right, not on showing of cause.
\par 
}
}
}
{\li0 \f2 \qj \b0 \ri0 \fs20 \cf1 \i0 
